  />

  <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6 mt-8">
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">
      <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> Waiting periods vary by insurer, plan, and individual circumstances. This guide provides general information only. Always verify specific waiting periods with insurance providers before purchasing coverage. We are not insurance brokers or licensed advisors.
    </p>
  </div>
</PageShell>
